dded `total_rows` to the runtime state dict so downstream consumers can calculate row position\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++**2. Master bus / Composer** (`duet_composer.py`)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- `_on_tracker_row` now writes `master_bus`, `section_curve`, and `automation_values` into composer state at every stride tick — not just at scene starts\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- `_on_scene_start` now also emits `section_curve` and `automation_values` from the start\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++**3. Sampler** (`sample_dsp_activity.py`)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Added `_row_bucket(self_state)` — divides scenes into early/mid/late thirds based on `tracker_row` / `tracker_total_rows`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- `_scene_profile` now varies by row bucket: Recap late → afterglow_residue, Theme late → emergence_motion\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Fixed a falsy-zero bug where `tracker_row=0` was coerced to `-1` via `or -1`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++**4. Self-listener** (`self_listener.py`)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Added `tracker_total_rows` to self-listener state output\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++**5. Face display** (`face_display.py`)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Renders section curve name and automation value bars from composer state\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++**6. Tests** (`test_row_automation.py`) — 11 new tests:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- `interpolate_automation_at_row` correctness\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Runtime state includes `total_rows`\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Automation updates fire beyond scene starts\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Master bus output shifts with automation values\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Row bucket early/mid/late classification\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Scene profile shifts for Recap, Theme, Development across buckets\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++- Automation curve in runtime state\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++**Validation**: 1831 tests pass, ruff clean on changed files, mypy clean.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n++AGE